<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Commission Earned!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            flex: 1;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .detail-value {
            flex: 2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoUrl || 'https://via.placeholder.com/150' %>" alt="<%= appName %>" class="logo">
        <h2>You've Earned a New Commission!</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Great news! You've earned a new commission from your referral.</p>
        
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <p style="margin: 0; text-align: center;">
                <span style="font-size: 14px;">New Commission</span><br>
                <span class="amount">$<%= amount %></span>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Order Number:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">#<%= orderNumber %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Commission Rate:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= commissionRate %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Total Earnings:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">$<%= totalEarnings %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Available Balance:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">$<%= availableBalance %></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your commission will be added to your available balance. Once you reach the minimum withdrawal amount, you can request a payout from your affiliate dashboard.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">View Your Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>Keep up the great work! The more you refer, the more you earn.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You're receiving this email because you're part of the <%= appName %> Affiliate Program.</p>
        <p><a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/affiliate/settings">Update notification preferences</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
